
'''Mireille Karera''' ni umunyarwandakazi w'umucuruzi akaba na rwiyemezamirimo , washinze kandi akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru wa KORA Coaching Group Ltd, isosiyete ikora ibya Coaching & Consulting ikorera mu [[Rwanda]] no [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] . <ref>https://www.lionessesofafrica.com/blog/2016/1/28/the-startup-story-of-mireille-karera</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/230914</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Karera yakurikiranye impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Business & Legal Translation i Cologne, mu [[Ubudage|Budage]] . <ref>https://www.rhrmo.org/2021/11/15/presenters-on-re-engineering-leadership-skills-for-human-resource-and-line-managers-through-coaching/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Kabera yagarutse muri [[Afurika]] nyuma yo kumara imyaka irenga 13 akora nk'uwambere mu kugurisha, ingamba zo guteza imbere ubucuruzi ku batanga serivisi z’imari ku isi nka Moody's Investor Services, EBS Dealing Resources (ubu ICAP) na Thomson Reuters i Londres, Dubai, Johannesburg na [[Nairobi]] . <ref>https://breakfastclubafrica.com/coaches-3/</ref> <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/madame-jeannette-kagame-yasabye-abagore-kwirinda-kwigana-imishinga-y-abandi</ref> Yabaye Umuyobozi w’Ihuriro ry’Abagore ku Isi mu [[Rwanda]] kandi mbere yari Umuyobozi w’Urugaga rw’Abagore ruherereye i Dubai ruha imbaraga abagore mu nshingano z’Ubuyobozi no kwiteza imbere ku kazi, <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/Inama-y-Abagore-ku-Isi-izizihiriza-Umunsi-w-Abagore-mu-Rwanda</ref> yagize uruhare mu gushyiraho gahunda z’ubujyanama bw’umwuga ku bagore. <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/magazine/karera-i-have-been-to-54-countries-so-far-1394656</ref> Afite inkuru nyinshi zishishikariza abagore kwishora mubucuruzi . <ref>http://hope-mag.com/index.php?com=news&option=read&ca=7&a=3889</ref> <ref>https://www.amazonswatchmagazine.com/exclusive-qa/my-dream-is-to-see-the-gender-agenda-become-a-thing-of-the-past-mireille-karera/</ref> Ubufatanye bwe hagati ya KORA Coaching Group na Career Women  Network [[Kigali]] bukemura ikibazo cyubumenyi hagati yabategarugori kugirango bahabwe amahirwe yo guhatanira akazi. <ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/rwanda-chosen-for-the-launch-of-kora-coaching</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/230914</ref> Isosiyete ye KORA Coaching and Business Academy (KCA) yakwirakwije serivisi zayo mu bihugu bitandukanye bya [[Afurika]]. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/local-leadership-coaching-company-looks-export-services-out-rwanda</ref> Mu by'ukuri, mu academy bituma abagore ba rwiyemezamirimo kubona uburenganzira business batoza no mentorship, ndetse ubumenyi gucunga ubucuruzi. <ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2019/06/first-lady-jeannette-kagame-advises-women-to-stop-replicating-business/</ref> <ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/91856/kigali-hateguwe-breakfast-seminar-yabagore-nabakobwa-bari-mu-nzego-zubuyobozi-mu-kubafasha-91856.html</ref>

== Ibihembo ==
Muri 2017, Karera yahawe igihembo "Africa’s Top 25 Distinguished Women in Business Excellence" n'ikinyamakuru Africa Leadership Magazine & Amazons Watch Magazine. <ref>https://www.rhrmo.org/2021/11/15/presenters-on-re-engineering-leadership-skills-for-human-resource-and-line-managers-through-coaching/</ref>

